<h3 class="sub-header">Why was Biblioglot made?</h3>
<div class="card-deck">
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title">There is Already an Abundance of Beginner Resources</h4>
      <p class="card-text">We all know languages learning apps like Duolingo and most of us have taken beginner classes in school. Once the basics are taught, students are left on their own to improve their language abilities.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title">Finding Native Speakers is Hard</h4>
      <p class="card-text">There's no shortcut. If you want to be fluent, you have to communicate with native speakers. However, it is difficult to find native speakers who are willing to invest time to help you unless you pay a hefty fee.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title">Going through Dictionary and Translation Service is Time-Consuming</h4>
      <p class="card-text">The traditional flipping through a dictionary for a definition is way too time-consuming. The act of copy-pasting to a translation service also takes away time from you learning the language.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
